{"tid":2266384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東張西望介紹完銀礦灣Staycation就大爆發","createTime":"2020-11-01T09:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T04:55:25.000Z","uid":12908,"like":57,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"47b45a876511d163ad01419510e0d399a639a0ed","tid":2266384,"uid":12908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:18:23.000Z","msg":"本港武漢肺炎疫情一直未能「清零」，昨日（31日）錄得3宗確診，全屬輸入，今日新增7宗確診，唯一一宗本地感染未能確定源頭，是一名42歲曾羈留旺角警署等拘留所、待遣返的中國籍女子。此外，本港暫錄得少於10宗初步確診，其中3人的感染源頭，來自梅窩銀礦灣海景度假樂園酒店的Staycation聚會。<br />\n<br />\n今日確診的待遣返42歲中國籍女子（第第5331號個案），於9月28日於警方行動中，因沒有有效逗留文件被捕，並於同入被拘留於旺角警署。她其後於10月30日被送至青山灣入境事務中心，數小時後被轉送至馬頭角羈留中心。該女子被捕前曾居於塘尾道東方泛達酒店，據報她長時間留在酒店內，少有外出，而她的抵港日期警方則仍在調查中。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201101/ZZ2TKQ7Q2NAFHHU6SIDHI7MX6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201101%2FZZ2TKQ7Q2NAFHHU6SIDHI7MX6I%2F&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh5ktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=f142053d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201101%2FZZ2TKQ7Q2NAFHHU6SIDHI7MX6I%2F&h=392dfcb3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201101/ZZ2TKQ7Q2NAFHHU6SIDHI7MX6I/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東張西望 | 不一樣的Staycation?! 大澳與梅窩酒店咁樣玩<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nNpfbon1exE&amp;ab_channel=TVBUSAOfficial\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnNpfbon1exE%26ab_channel%3DTVBUSAOfficial&d=Xh6WvVyDZ%2Fzj0BED8lYnh5ktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=ab3396d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nNpfbon1exE&amp;ab_channel=TVBUSAOfficial</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe77f6c7421a5928683af7fc916a6116bf18252c","tid":2266384,"uid":12908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T09:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" cl